          "AUTHORIZATION"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "(?:issuer|ISSUER)[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*[\"']https://[a-zA-Z0-9._-]+\\.okta(?:preview)?\\.com[\"'][,\\s]+[^\\n]{0,150}client_secret[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*[\"']([A-Za-z0-9_-]{40,80})[\"']",
        "message": "Okta OIDC configuration with hardcoded client secret detected. Okta OIDC configurations containing both issuer URL and client secret expose complete authentication credentials. This allows attackers to authenticate as your application, obtain access tokens for user impersonation, and bypass security controls. Remove hardcoded secrets and use secure configuration management.",
